'''钛酸'''是一类由[[钛|钛]]、[[氢|氢]]和[[氧|氧]]组成的化合物，通式为 [TiO<sub>''x''</sub>(OH)<sub>4−2''x''</sub>]<sub>''n''</sub>。 它们主要描述于较早的文献中，已经合成了各种简单的钛酸。这些材料都没有晶体学和只有很少的光谱学支持。一些较老的文献，包括 Brauer's Handbook ，把 TiO<sub>2</sub> 也视作一种钛酸。<ref name="Fresenius1887">{{cite book|author=C. Remigius Fresenius|title=Qualitative Chemical Analysis|url=https://archive.org/details/qualitativechem00grovgoog|year=1887|publisher=J. & A. Churchill|pages=[https://archive.org/details/qualitativechem00grovgoog/page/n141 115]–116}}</ref>

==各种钛酸==
*[[偏钛酸|偏钛酸]] ({{Chem|H|2|TiO|3}})<ref>{{cite journal |journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society |volume=13 |issue=7 |pages=210–211 |author=F.P. Dunnington |title=On metatitanic acid and the estimation of titanium by hydrogen peroxide |year=1891 |doi=10.1021/ja02124a032 |url=https://zenodo.org/record/1428963 }}</ref> 
*原钛酸 ({{Chem|H|4|TiO|4}})<ref>{{cite book |title=Salts and their reactions: A class-book of practical chemistry |author= Leonard Dobbin, Hugh Marshall |publisher=University of Edinburgh | year=1904 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=WCBIAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA172&dq=review+orthotitanic+acid#q=review%20orthotitanic%20acid}}</ref>被描述为白色盐状粉末，类似 TiO<sub>2</sub>·2.16H<sub>2</sub>O<ref>{{cite book|first=P. |last=Ehrlich |chapter=Titanium(IV) Oxide Hydrate TiO<sub>2</sub>·''n''H<sub>2</sub>O |title= Handbook of Preparative Inorganic Chemistry |edition=2nd |editor-first=G. |editor-last=Brauer |publisher=Academic Press |date=1963 |location=New York |volume= 1 |page= 1218}}</ref>
*过氧钛酸 ({{Chem|Ti(OH)|3|O|2|H}}) 被描述为可以由[[二氧化钛|二氧化钛]]和[[硫酸|硫酸]]和[[过氧化氢|过氧化氢]]反应生成的黄色固体。它会散发 O<sub>2</sub>并分解。<ref>{{cite book|first=P. |last=Ehrlich |chapter=Peroxotitanic Acid H<sub>4</sub>TiO<sub>5</sub>|title= Handbook of Preparative Inorganic Chemistry |edition=2nd |editor-first=G. |editor-last=Brauer |publisher=Academic Press |date=1963 |location=New York |volume= 1 |page= 1219}}</ref>
*高钛酸 (TiO(H<sub>2</sub>O<sub>2</sub>)<sup>2+</sup>)<ref>{{cite journal |journal= [[Fresenius'_Journal_of_Analytical_Chemistry|Fresenius' Journal of Analytical Chemistry]] |year= 1967 |volume= 229 |issue= 6 |pages= 413–433 |title= Analysis using fluotitanic acid-hydrogen peroxide reagent: A review |first= Hisao |last= Fukamauchi |doi= 10.1007/BF00505508 |s2cid= 92389986 }}</ref>

